scene.message:
SP: Humans, who hate and kill{nl}
one another, fouling even the{nl}
planet they live on to sate{nl}
their desires...{waitkey}{clearbox}As living things, they were{nl}
a failure after all!!{waitkey}{ret}

SP: I wonder if the family I{nl}
left back home is well.{waitkey}I should quit a job like{nl}
this.{waitkey}{ret}

SP: Humans, in the end, think{nl}
of nothing but themselves!{waitkey}{clearbox}They'd be better off wiped{nl}
from the face of the earth!!{waitkey}{ret}
